            <lg xml:id="TK1112">
<l>malarkāṇiṉ maiyātti neñcē yivaḷkaṇ </l>
<l>palarkāṇum pūvokku meṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul, fancying that flowers which are seen by many can resemble her eyes, you become confused at the sight of them.</l>
